@{
	ViewData["Title"] = "Listening";
	Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout1.cshtml";
}
<div class="col-md-6 border-right overflow-auto">
	<div class="section p-3" id="listening">
		<h3 class="text-center">Listening Section</h3>
		<p style="text-align: justify;">
			You will hear a short lecture about renewable energy. Listen and fill in the blanks with the correct word or phrase.
		</p>
		<p style="text-align: justify;">
			Lecturer: "Renewable energy sources are becoming increasingly important in our effort to combat climate change. Solar energy, for instance, harnesses energy from the sun using solar panels. Wind energy captures the power of the wind with turbines. Both of these sources are <b>(1)</b> and do not produce harmful emissions. Another key source is hydroelectric power, which generates electricity from the <b>(2)</b> of water. All these renewable sources are crucial for reducing our reliance on fossil fuels and mitigating the impact of global warming."
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6 overflow-auto">
	<div class="section p-3" id="listening-answers">
		<h3>Questions:</h3>
		<p>1. Solar and wind energy sources are <input type="text" name="q1"></p>
		<p>2. Hydroelectric power generates electricity from the <input type="text" name="q2"> of water.</p>
	</div>
</div>

